    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a method based on an Alternate-Marking technique to perform packet loss, delay, and jitter measurements on live traffic. This technology can be applied in various situations and for different protocols. It could be considered Passive or Hybrid depending on the application. This document obsoletes [RFC8321].</t>
